    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对杜沃斯帝国的威胁，自由联盟发起了“边境计划”。作为该计划的先行者，您将负责建设北部边境的一个定居点。您的使命是建造城市、招募伙伴、开拓土地，将您的定居点发展成为边境上最繁华的城镇。在这片充满希望与挑战的土地上，您将引领一场难忘的探险，结识朋友，甚至邂逅真爱。我们期待这段旅程能够成为您难忘的记忆！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/e57f6f02116e19729413a56fff9b281a.avif?t=1770190441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras_big/e57f6f02116e19729413a56fff9b281a.webp?t=1770190441 width=1600 height=1973 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/eee65a97eb104112a14301c020f67e0e.avif?t=1770190441\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作将迎来三十多位各具特色的NPC，其中十位是“核心”攻略对象（其中四位是由众筹玩家选出），还有十多位其他可攻略对象，您可以在定居点与他们建立深厚的友谊，与部分NPC擦出爱情的火花。精细的建模和生动的交互，加上丰富的故事线，将为您留下难忘的梦幻回忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下面是我们核心浪漫角色穿着睡衣的特别原画作品，作为新年的特别礼物送给大家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/6ec64d8f109abc31571222f19348f5b5.avif?t=1770190441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras_big/6ec64d8f109abc31571222f19348f5b5.avif?t=1770190441 width=800 height=795 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/589c81a3cea483f1a3aee7d353252aaa.avif?t=1770190441\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >继《沙石镇时光》与《波西亚时光》的故事之后，自由城市联盟与杜沃斯帝国的紧张关系日益升级。在“边境计划”的号召下，新的英雄和反派相继登场，帝国的威胁与过去的谜团交织。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这片土地的未来，掌握在您的手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/60b371c076f4b83d6057fa4a646220b5.poster.avif?t=1770190441\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/60b371c076f4b83d6057fa4a646220b5.webm?t=1770190441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/7e6f652664f92ab9f8f2d69994fade0d.avif?t=1770190441\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为定居点的负责人，您拥有绝对的权力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决定招募对象、建造设施与建筑、管理人事，甚至任命亲信于要职。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择三名定居者作为您的亲密伙伴，他们将与您并肩作战，执行您的指令。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但请谨慎处理与追随者之间的私人关系，以免引发不必要的麻烦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/c3d7b5303bf8b2f41c94259159de21cc.poster.avif?t=1770190441\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/c3d7b5303bf8b2f41c94259159de21cc.webm?t=1770190441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/45d08701c8a99426b11d3317041ce901.avif?t=1770190441\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供多种预制建筑供您选择，或者您可以亲自动手，从奠基到完工，一步步打造独一无二的建筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的追随者和居民将是您最好的建筑助手，共同创造出您梦中的家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/8176a18c14614f416cc62b07d9b553a2.poster.avif?t=1770190441\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/8176a18c14614f416cc62b07d9b553a2.webm?t=1770190441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/5831fa1472f4334f02cb1d5ee19b3feb.avif?t=1770190441\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《时光3：永耀之境》支持1-4人多人合作模式，无缝融合单人游戏体验。与好友一同体验剧情、建设城镇、招募伙伴、参与战斗、经历浪漫时刻，探索神秘副本，共同绘制属于你们的永耀之境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/6e5a99149aefd7f7a9e145c069828295.poster.avif?t=1770190441\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/6e5a99149aefd7f7a9e145c069828295.webm?t=1770190441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199500/extras/67d94dd8770b4d2058348944fee6a2bd.avif?t=1770190441\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 角色个性化：自由打造您的角色形象，让您的角色更加与众不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 画面升级：创新的美术流程和艺术风格，带来独树一帜的视觉体验和细致入微的场景描绘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 节日庆典：享受丰富多彩的节日活动和小游戏，增添游戏的乐趣和多样性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 探索新方式：体验全新的探索模式，您可以在游戏中攀爬和滑翔，探索每一个角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 更多故事线：解锁丰富的支线剧情，深入游戏世界的每一个细节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 惊喜连连：还有无数惊喜等您在游戏中亲自发掘，每一次游玩都有新的发现。</p>",
